OL,3,CFresh CCTV appeal launched after man
OL,4,Cfound dead on common
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the death of
OL,7,Fa Polish man whose body was found in a
OL,8,Fnature reserve on Southampton Common
OL,9,Fhave arrested two men on suspicion of
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FThe remains of Ernest Deputat, 45,
OL,13,Fwere discovered on 8 October 2025 on
OL,14,Fwoodland near where a fire had been
OL,15,Fstarted.
OL,17,FHe'd been living off grid and was
OL,18,Fknown among the homeless community.
OL,20,FTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,21,Fmurder were bailed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
