OL,3,CFresh CCTV appeal launched after man
OL,4,Cfound dead on common
OL,6,FPolice have released a CCTV image of a
OL,7,Fwoman with her dog, who they believe
OL,8,Fmay have witnessed something important
OL,9,Fconnected to their investigation.
OL,11,FThe woman in the image, was seen
OL,12,Fwalking a dog on Southampton Common on
OL,13,Fthe morning of Saturday 6 May.
OL,15,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"We would urge her, or anyone who
OL,17,Fknows her identity, to please get in
OL,18,Ftouch with us at the earliest
OL,19,Fopportunity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782042480
OL,3,CFresh CCTV appeal launched after man
OL,4,Cfound dead on common
OL,6,F"It is possible that this woman has
OL,7,Falready been previously spoken to by
OL,8,Finvestigators.
OL,10,F"However, as part of new information
OL,11,Freceived and further developments in
OL,12,Four investigation, we would like to
OL,13,Fspeak to her once more.
OL,15,F"If you were also in the area of
OL,16,FSouthampton Common on the morning of
OL,17,FSaturday 6 September, please get in
OL,18,Fcontact with us.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
