FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782042480
OL,3,CFresh CCTV appeal launched after man
OL,4,Cfound dead on common
OL,6,F"We are particularly keen to hear from
OL,7,Fany dog walkers who are still yet to
OL,8,Fcome forward.
OL,10,F"No matter how small or insignificant
OL,11,Fyou think the information may be, it
OL,12,Fcould be key to our investigation."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
